title: POMEPS Conversations: Michael Wahid Hanna & Thanassis Cambanis (S. 4, Ep. 2)
itunes:author: Marc Lynch
itunes:summary: The George Washington University's Marc Lynch, director of the Project on Middle East Political Science, with Michael Wahid Hanna & Thanassis Cambanis of The Century Foundation. They talk about the upcoming fifth anniversary of the Egyptian revolution on January 25, and the challenges facing Egypt today.
